[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":196},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20190630\u002F2768809875\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20190630\u002F2768809875\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20190630\u002F2768809875\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20190630\u002F2768809875\u002F":171,"related:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20190630\u002F2768809875\u002F":180},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F30\u002Fnodejs-express-template-engines\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":155,"date":156,"description":18,"extension":157,"lang":158,"meta":159,"navigation":72,"path":160,"readingMinutes":161,"seo":162,"standalone":163,"stem":164,"tags":165,"tldr":168,"updated":168,"url":169,"__hash__":170},"content\u002F全端勇士之路 Node.js\u002F全端勇士之路-Node-js-基礎學習-Express-template-篇.md","全端勇士之路 Node.js 基礎學習-Express template 篇","2768809875",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":149},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,30,38,92,95,105,109,112,134,142,145],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"新的章節又開啟了，接下來將會講到 template，tempalte 在開發上是非常常見的一個技術，所以這邊這篇就先來介紹一下吧",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"template-語言","template 語言",[16,24,25],{},"以往我們開發前端都是靜態的 HTML 頁面，當若頁面有 100 頁，那可能有一天 header 要做調整，那就變成要調整 100 頁，其實這對於開發來講非常的沒有效率，所以就出現了 template 這個東西，那業界常見的 template 又有那些呢?這邊來主要介紹兩個",[12,27,29],{"id":28},"ejs-template","EJS template",[16,31,32,33,37],{},"如果是新手入門的話，我建議使用 EJS　template，因為與寫 HTML 並沒有太大的差異，所以學習曲線上是比較低的，那叫做 template 語言，所以它就可以寫一些變數、迴圈或是設置 layout，舉例來講，若要傳入變數或撰寫程式碼，都會使用 ",[34,35,36],"code",{},"\u003C% %>"," 包覆",[39,40,45],"pre",{"className":41,"code":42,"language":43,"meta":44,"style":44},"language-ejs shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","\u003Cp>\n\u003C% title %>\n\u003C\u002Fp>\n\n\u003C% if (user) { %>\n  \u003Ch2>\u003C%= user.name %>\u003C\u002Fh2>\n\u003C% } %>\n","ejs","",[34,46,47,55,61,67,74,80,86],{"__ignoreMap":44},[48,49,52],"span",{"class":50,"line":51},"line",1,[48,53,54],{},"\u003Cp>\n",[48,56,58],{"class":50,"line":57},2,[48,59,60],{},"\u003C% title %>\n",[48,62,64],{"class":50,"line":63},3,[48,65,66],{},"\u003C\u002Fp>\n",[48,68,70],{"class":50,"line":69},4,[48,71,73],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":72},true,"\n",[48,75,77],{"class":50,"line":76},5,[48,78,79],{},"\u003C% if (user) { %>\n",[48,81,83],{"class":50,"line":82},6,[48,84,85],{},"  \u003Ch2>\u003C%= user.name %>\u003C\u002Fh2>\n",[48,87,89],{"class":50,"line":88},7,[48,90,91],{},"\u003C% } %>\n",[16,93,94],{},"這樣就是代表一個程式碼區間的意思",[16,96,97,98],{},"那它每一種標籤的形式都不太一樣，這邊可以去",[99,100,104],"a",{"href":101,"rel":102},"https:\u002F\u002Fejs.bootcss.com\u002F",[103],"nofollow","官網看更詳細",[12,106,108],{"id":107},"jadepug-template","jade\u002Fpug template",[16,110,111],{},"若要拿 EJS 與 pug 做比較的話，好比 SCSS VS SASS，大家都知道後者 SASS 的學習曲線會較 SCSS 高，那 PUG 也是，而 PUG 撰寫的方式稍微有點不太一樣，會非常的簡寫，程式碼區間則是沒有特別的標記符號，但變數則是使用等於(=)",[39,113,117],{"className":114,"code":115,"language":116,"meta":44,"style":44},"language-pug shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","ul\n  each val in [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]\n    li= val\n","pug",[34,118,119,124,129],{"__ignoreMap":44},[48,120,121],{"class":50,"line":51},[48,122,123],{},"ul\n",[48,125,126],{"class":50,"line":57},[48,127,128],{},"  each val in [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]\n",[48,130,131],{"class":50,"line":63},[48,132,133],{},"    li= val\n",[16,135,136,137],{},"如果想更了解的話可以看看",[99,138,141],{"href":139,"rel":140},"https:\u002F\u002Fpugjs.org\u002Fapi\u002Fgetting-started.html",[103],"官網",[16,143,144],{},"基本上這兩種 template 都可以了解一下，畢竟各有好壞。",[146,147,148],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":44,"searchDepth":57,"depth":57,"links":150},[151,152,1